data.description: Perfectly set on a tree shaded lot, this Hartsville beauty feels like home as soon as you pull up. Just minutes from town, this exquisitely maintained home has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  Enjoy your morning coffee on your fully screened in private porch. Back yard is fenced in for complete privacy. Built in desk and bookshelves make for a nice home office area. This home features a security system with cameras as well. Large yard on a corner lot. HVAC is 2 years old with a 20 year warranty. You don't want to miss this one. Call your Realtor today for an appointment to make this your new home!
